Additional notes:

The clinical reference data seeded under `schema/02_seed_from_handbook.sql`
is sourced from the Rwanda Biomedical Centre's 2024 Integrated Malaria
Control Guidelines, and the teaching-mode baseline (`schema/09_who_baseline.sql`)
is sourced from the WHO Global Malaria Programme Guidelines for Malaria (2024).
Both source documents are publicly available from their respective publishers.
MalariaChat redistributes this data only as reference material under fair use
for educational purposes; the data itself is the property of RBC and WHO
respectively, not of MalariaChat or its contributors.

The LLM integration in `llm.abe` (Anthropic by default) requires the user to
supply their own API key. No key is bundled with this software.
